-- Sanz Pancko Dental Clinic - English-speaking dental clinic in Barcelona
('Sanz Pancko Dental Clinic', 'Dentists', 'English-speaking dental clinic in Barcelona''s El Clot neighborhood. Founded by Dr. Sanz and Dr. Pancko, with Dr. Pancko being from the USA, the clinic is a reference for English-speaking patients seeking dental care in Barcelona. Specialized team offers comprehensive dental services including general dentistry, periodontics (gum disease treatment), endodontics (root canals), prosthodontics (crowns, bridges, dentures), maxillofacial surgery, implantology (dental implants), and dental whitening (teeth bleaching). All treatments are planned and supervised by Dr. Sanz and Dr. Pancko, focusing on both patient needs and dental health. Offers conscious sedation administered by specialized anesthesiologists for patients with dental phobia or requiring complex treatments. Provides personalized and efficient treatment with a team of dentists dedicated exclusively to their specialties. Conveniently located near Clot metro station (L1, L2). Monday to Friday hours: 9:00 AM - 8:30 PM.', 'C/ Rogent 40-42 local 2, 08026 Barcelona', 'Barcelona', 'Barcelona', '+34 932 469 043', 'info@clinicadentalsyp.com', 'https://www.clinicadentalsyp.com', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
